com.microsoft.azure.management.network

Class NetworkResourceProviderClientImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.windowsazure.core.ServiceClient<NetworkResourceProviderClient>
      • com.microsoft.azure.management.network.NetworkResourceProviderClientImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    NetworkResourceProviderClient, FilterableService<NetworkResourceProviderClient>, Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public class NetworkResourceProviderClientImpl
extends ServiceClient<NetworkResourceProviderClient>
implements NetworkResourceProviderClient
    The Windows Azure Network management API provides a RESTful set of web services that interact with Windows Azure Networks service to manage your network resrources. The API has entities that capture the relationship between an end user and the Windows Azure Networks service.
